{"tid":1858283,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"【武漢肺炎】中證監連夜通知券商 A股復市禁止沽空","createTime":"2020-02-02T15:20:04.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-02T17:37:57.000Z","uid":38255,"like":112,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":67,"replies":[{"pid":"ce489b76e72ef7c0e5510fd4f8018bdf8dc9585e","tid":1858283,"uid":38255,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-02T15:20:04.000Z","msg":"武漢肺炎疫情擴散，A股開市前夕再演暴力救市。據內地《21世紀經濟報道》引述消息指，中國證監會今日晚上對多家券商發出通知，要求由明天（3日）起暫停融券賣出業務，意味A股將暫停沽空交易。<br />\n<br />\n根據網上流傳一間內地券商的指示文件，指今次暫停沽空是「抗擊肺炎、穩定市場的政治任務」，公司務必要「嚴肅對待、全力配合」，要求各營業部門盡快通知客戶，「做好客戶的思想工作」。"},{"pid":"2553e188b36969b37762b35eb94cfdb2b0f39fa8","tid":1858283,"uid":45821,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-02T15:20:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2lny/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2lny/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2lny/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2lny/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2lny/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2lny/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2lny/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2lny/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2lny/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2lny/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"17ee2666703001cb1dd0da7d865d124ebddf4803","tid":1858283,"uid":15703,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-02T15:20:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d23da2d88a656d108b44ce2e42ddeac80e720bca","tid":1858283,"uid":12558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-02T15:20:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"17af0540edf13b4afab0aec87d565647ba27170